Turkey’s Galatasaray Begins Talks to Transfer Pino to Saudi

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-08-27T09:39:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-27/turkey-s-galatasaray-begins-talks-to-transfer-pino-to-saudi.html
Turkish soccer club Galatasaray has
begun negotiations to transfer Colombian winger Juan Pablo Pino
Puello to Saudi club Nassr Saudi FC, according to a statement to
the  Istanbul Stock Exchange  from Galatasaray’s merchandising
arm.  The transfer would be “temporary,” the statement said
without giving further details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  